	(text "R13, R10 = 0ohm\nC11, C12 = DNI\nthe above changes were made in the assumption that\nthe issue was the filtering circuit. It turned out\nI had a bad solder joint on one of the pullup \nresistors. I have applied heavy software filtering\nand getting good results. Re-applying the original \nvalues and reducing the software filtering could\nbe interesting and potentially improve performance"
